Method Detail

getTransformedContext

IContext getTransformedContext(IContext context)
                               throws ThinklabException
Return the context that this observation will have once transformed in the passed context. Should not actually perform the transformation if at all possible. If that is necessary in order to know the context, it should store the result and return when transform() is called. The preferred way is to compute the transformation when transform() is called, so that context extraction can be done quickly.

Returns:
Throws:
ThinklabException
